---
import { homePhotos } from '../../data/home';
---

<section class="crossover" data-screen-label="For owners">
  <img class="crossover__bg" src={homePhotos['living-fireplace']} alt="" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
  <div class="crossover__inner">
    <div class="reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Own a home in San Diego?</p>
      <h2>Guests love the stay. Owners love the returns.</h2>
      <p>The same care that makes a guest rebook is what keeps your calendar full and your reviews at five stars. If this is how you'd want your home run — let's talk.</p>
      <div class="crossover__stats">
        <div class="crossover__stat"><div class="v">+51%</div><div class="l">avg. over market</div></div>
        <div class="crossover__stat"><div class="v">$80M+</div><div class="l">under management</div></div>
        <div class="crossover__stat"><div class="v">Since 2013</div><div class="l">San Diego Superhost</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="crossover__actions reveal">
      <a href="/owners#estimate" class="btn btn-lg">Schedule a consultation</a>
      <a href="/owners" class="btn btn-ghost-light btn-lg">Learn about management</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="crossover__owners" style="position:relative;z-index:2;max-width:var(--container);margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px;">
    <p class="eyebrow reveal" style="color:#fff;justify-content:center;text-align:center">What owners say</p>
    <div class="ownrev reveal">
      <div class="ownrev__card">
        <div class="ownrev__stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="ownrev__text">Hands down the best management company in San Diego. They salvaged a rental of mine while I was living out of state — broken fridge on the 4th of July, a gas leak — and handled it all while keeping the reviews coming.</p>
        <div class="ownrev__who"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500648767791-00dcc994a43e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=120&q=80" alt="Sean M." loading="lazy" decoding="async" /><div><div class="ownrev__name">Sean M.</div><div class="ownrev__home">Owner · Mission Beach</div></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="ownrev__card">
        <div class="ownrev__stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="ownrev__text">Their design team restyled the whole house before launch and the photos are unreal. We booked 26 nights the first month at a rate I genuinely didn't think was possible for our place.</p>
        <div class="ownrev__who"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544005313-94ddf0286df2?auto=format&fit=crop&w=120&q=80" alt="Priya &amp; Sam" loading="lazy" decoding="async" /><div><div class="ownrev__name">Priya &amp; Sam</div><div class="ownrev__home">Owners · La Jolla</div></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="ownrev__card">
        <div class="ownrev__stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="ownrev__text">Switched from a national manager and my net was up double digits in the first quarter. The statements are so clear I finally stopped second-guessing every line. They protect the home like it's their own.</p>
        <div class="ownrev__who"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506794778202-cad84cf45f1d?auto=format&fit=crop&w=120&q=80" alt="Marcus T." loading="lazy" decoding="async" /><div><div class="ownrev__name">Marcus T.</div><div class="ownrev__home">Owner · Pacific Beach</div></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
